<li><a href="/wiki/1939_%C3%A0_la_t%C3%A9l%C3%A9vision" title="1939 à la télévision">1939</a>&#160;: <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Passion,_Poison_and_Petrifaction&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Passion, Poison and Petrifaction (page inexistante)">Passion, Poison and Petrifaction</a></i> (TV)</li>
