ankiewicz" title="Joseph L. Mankiewicz">Joseph L. Mankiewicz</a> (1950)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Joseph_L._Mankiewicz" title="Joseph L. Mankiewicz">Joseph L. Mankiewicz</a> (1951)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Harry_Brown_(%C3%A9crivain)" title="Harry Brown (écrivain)">Harry Brown</a> et <a href="/wiki/Michael_Wilson_(sc%C3%A9nariste)" title="Michael Wilson (scénariste)">Michael Wilson</a> (1952)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Charles_Schnee" title="Charles Schnee">Charles Schnee</a> (1953)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Daniel_Taradash" title="Daniel Taradash">Daniel Taradash</a> (1954)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/George_Seaton" title="George Seaton">George Seaton</a> (1955)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Paddy_Chayefsky" title="Paddy Chayefsky">Paddy Chayefsky</a> (1956)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/John_Farrow" title="John Farrow">John Farrow</a>, <a href="/wiki/S.J._Perelman" title="S.J. Perelman">S.J. Perelman</a> et <a href="/wiki/James_Poe" title="James Poe">James Poe</a> (1957)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Carl_Foreman" title="Carl Foreman">Carl Foreman</a> et <a href="/wiki/Michael_Wilson_(sc%C3%A9nariste)" title="Michael Wilson (scénariste)">Michael Wilson</a> (1958)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alan_Jay_Lerner" title="Alan Jay Lerner">Alan Jay Lerner</a> (1959)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Neil_Paterson" title="Neil Paterson">Neil Paterson</a> (1960)</span></td>
